# YouTube Electron App ðŸŽ¬

A desktop-like YouTube wrapper app built with Electron.js. It provides an app-style experience for YouTube, bypasses browser-level filters (like CleanBrowsing), and opens without a visible terminal window.

---

## ðŸš€ Features

- Runs YouTube as a standalone desktop app
- Login handled via default browser (resolves DNS filter login issues)
- No command prompt window using `.vbs` launcher
- Silent startup
- Looks and feels like the real YouTube

---

## ðŸ›  Tech Stack

- [Electron.js](https://www.electronjs.org/)
- Custom `.bat` and `.vbs` scripting for smoother UX

